title: Bibiana on Her Journey of Self-Healing
description:
Rachel is joined once again by co-host Krystal Nielson! The women talk to “Bachelor” alum Bibiana Julian about her journey of wellness and healing over the last couple of years. She reveals how she crawled out of that dark place to find happiness and feel good about herself once again. 

Be sure to rate and subscribe so you never miss an episode.
